### 결제 요청 (POST /api/v1/payments)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/payments
Content-Type: application/json
X-Loopers-LoginId: testuser
X-Loopers-LoginPw: Password123!

{
  "orderId": 1,
  "cardType": "SAMSUNG",
  "cardNo": "1234-5678-9012-3456"
}

